data.description: 40 ACRES WITH 2 PONDS! 3 Bedroom 2 1/2 Bath brick ranch home sits just outside Central Community.  Wood floors throughout main living areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Spacious rooms ready for you to move in. In addition property has garage, barn, and covered parking for tractor or RV.  Country living with room to grow!
